CS Military Specialist
A Coalition States soldier with advanced training beyond the standard grunt.
Military Specialists are the officers and elite infantry of the CS Army,
trained in tactics, leadership, and advanced weapons systems.

They choose from Military, Weapons, Physical, and Technical skill categories.
Military Specialists receive broader equipment access than standard CS Grunts
and are trained to lead small unit operations.

Attribute requirements: IQ 10, ME 8, PS 10.
Starting equipment: Coalition grunt armor, CP-40 laser rifle, personal radio,
standard field kit, and a set of military-issue credentials.
